version_description: Correct chords and chord names, due to the variants used in the chorus.
As this song does not contain guitar, this is a transcription of the chords played by the piano.
Timing is in 4. For the intro, verse and outro F is 4 four beats, Bb is 2 and C is 2. All chords in chorus are 4 beats each.

Strum D7 D6 D7 D Once and then strum G and A7 multiple times. Hope you enjoy this version of the song. In my opinion this is easier and more accurate than the other F Bb and C version. Also,to submit the tab I had to put the key down as E but that is probably wrong. Composed by using Djence's youtube video. The videos link - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=P1CbOeEuwE4 Watch video for timing.
Capo on 3 based on the studio version here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RheJW2nhkb8.
